<section id="aureline-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 col-md-8">
        <h3 class="aureline-overview-title">Overview</h3>
        <div class="aureline-overview-text">
          Charles is a talented engineer<br>
          If you want to buy something on a website, just pull out your smartphone and scan the QR code on the screen. The checkout (shipping / billing addresses) and payment is done for you.<br>  
          You also get an instant confirmation on your smartphone and on the webpage.<br><br>
          With a single app you can pay on your computer, tablet, and on your phone (directly through the app this time).
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to image_tag("charles1.jpg", alt: "Random"), '' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>


<section id="onesnap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 col-md-8">
        <h3 class="onesnap-title">Onesnap (2014)</h3>
        <div class="onesnap-text">
          Onesnap is a mobile payment system that can be used for fast and painless checkouts on eCommerce websites.<br>
          If you want to buy something on a website, just pull out your smartphone and scan the QR code on the screen. The checkout (shipping / billing addresses) and payment is done for you.<br>  
          You also get an instant confirmation on your smartphone and on the webpage.<br><br>
          With a single app you can pay on your computer, tablet, and on your phone (directly through the app this time).
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to image_tag("onesnap-logo.png", alt: "Random"), '' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-0 col-sm-1 col-md-2"></div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
    <%= link_to image_tag("onesnap-how-it-works.png", alt: "Onesnap how it works"), '' %>
  </ul>
</div>

</section>


<section id="intown">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to image_tag("intown-logo.png", alt: "Random"), '' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 col-md-8">
        <h3 class="intown-title">Intown (2012)</h3>
        <div class="intown-text">
          Intown was a smartphone app project that won several prizes in startup idea contests. <br>The team was composed of Jean-Charles Gasche, Aur√©line Grange and Pablo Klemm. <br>
          Intown is a smartphone application that allows you to buy drinks and show tickets for your friends, wherever they are in the world. Let's imagine you are in Switzerland and hear about a friend being in New York. You now remember a really cool rooftop bar you went to and where the bartender did those incredible cocktails with Cognac and Martini! Your friend should definitely go to that bar! <br><br>
          (1) You pull out your phone, you select the bar in the app, and buy that precise cocktail in the list that appears.<br>
          (2) Your friend receives a QR code on his phone to present to the bartender.<br>
          (3) Your friend enjoys his drink!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-0 col-sm-1 col-md-1"></div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-md-10">
    <%= link_to image_tag("intown-how-it-works.png", alt: "Intown how it works"), '' %>
  </ul>
</div>

</section>



